snippet.title: Amber Heard Officially Charged With Perjury & Faces 4 Years In Prison
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Officially Charged With Perjury & Faces 4 Years In Prison
As you hopefully have seen, we've been covering the case between Amber Heard and Johnny Depp for...well...a very long time. Mainly because every time you turn around something new appears to be going on. From certain cases being ended due to lack of evidence, new evidence popping up, new testimony stating one thing or another, or just how the two react to everything, things keep evolving. And that brings us to now, because sources are saying that Amber Heard might be in serious trouble based on the results of evidence presented by LAPD and Johnny Depp recently. We'll break it down for you. Be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!

Click HERE To Enter The GIVEAWAY! 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC76r9K-_Knc7d38c9uKRwaw?sub_confirmation=1 

And there you have it, everyone! A look at the situation that might honestly be brewing for Amber Heard based on the evidence of the body cam footage. Do you think that she will honestly will be checked out for perjury? And if so, could this be the break that Johnny Depp needs to really start turning things around? Let us know in the comments below, be sure to subscribe and we'll see you next time on the channel!
